    "title": {
      "rendered": "5 Trends in Nonprofit Infographic Design"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/5-trends-in-nonprofit-infographic-design.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-15887\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"5 trends in nonprofit infographic design\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/5-trends-in-nonprofit-infographic-design-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/5-trends-in-nonprofit-infographic-design.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/5-trends-in-nonprofit-infographic-design.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/5-trends-in-nonprofit-infographic-design.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/5-trends-in-nonprofit-infographic-design.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/5-trends-in-nonprofit-infographic-design.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>As the fiscal year comes to a close and nonprofits are currently crafting next year&#8217;s budget, adding a line item for infographic design would be a very wise investment. From print fundraising appeals to digital annuals reports to compelling storytelling through tweets and status updates, the social science of online behavior confirms again and again that messages are most effectively communicated through images.\u00a0Custom infographic design fees vary widely depending on complexity (ranging from $1-10,000), but a creative, Adobe Photoshop-skilled new media manager can customize <a href=\"http://www.shutterstock.com/cat.mhtml?searchterm=infographic&amp;search_group=&amp;lang=en&amp;language=en&amp;search_source=search_form&amp;version=llv1\">stock infographics</a> or no matter your design experience, utilize services like <a href=\"http://piktochart.com/\">Piktochart</a>, <a href=\"http://infogr.am/\">Infogram</a>, and <a href=\"http://www.easel.ly/\">easelly</a>. That said, the technology of infographics are evolving quickly. They can now be designed in video format, animated, and <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/2014/02/25/11-responsively-designed-nonprofit-websites-to-study-and-learn-from/\">responsively designed</a> to ensure mobile compatibility.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">1. Video Infographics<br />\nWatch: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gQelgbDlhuw\">WildAid Elephant Infographic</a></h2>\n<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/gQelgbDlhuw\" height=\"315\" width=\"600\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">2. Responsive Infographics<br />\nView: <a href=\"http://www.hsi.org/issues/becrueltyfree/facts/infographic/en/index.html\">Creating a Cruelty-Free World</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.hsi.org/issues/becrueltyfree/facts/infographic/en/index.html\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-15871\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Cruelty Free\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Cruelty-Free.png?resize=600%2C357\" width=\"600\" height=\"357\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Cruelty-Free.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Cruelty-Free.png?resize=300%2C178&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">3. Animated .GIF Infographics a.k.a. Animagraffs<br />\nView:\u00a0<a href=\"http://animagraffs.com/cheetah-natures-speed-machine/\">Cheetah: Nature&#8217;s Speed Machine</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://animagraffs.com/cheetah-natures-speed-machine/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-15869\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Cheetah Inforgraphic\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Cheetah-Inforgraphic.png?resize=600%2C358\" width=\"600\" height=\"358\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Cheetah-Inforgraphic.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Cheetah-Inforgraphic.png?resize=300%2C179&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">4. Annual Report Infographics<br />\nView: <a href=\"http://www.richertschnorr.com/new-york-public-library-annual-report/\">New York Public Library Annual Report</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.richertschnorr.com/new-york-public-library-annual-report/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15877\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Annual report Infographic nonprofit\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Annual-report-Infographic-nonprofit.png?resize=600%2C400\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Annual-report-Infographic-nonprofit.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Annual-report-Infographic-nonprofit.png?resize=300%2C200&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">5. Press Release Infographics<br />\nView: <a href=\"http://www.prdaily.com/Main/Articles/Infographics_as_press_releases_3_beautiful_example_16145.aspx\">Infographics as Press Releases</a></h2>\n<p><a style=\"text-align: center;\" href=\"http://www.prdaily.com/Main/Articles/Infographics_as_press_releases_3_beautiful_example_16145.aspx\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-15875\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Press Release\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Press-Release.png?resize=600%2C406\" width=\"600\" height=\"406\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Press-Release.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/Press-Release.png?resize=300%2C203&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;\"><em>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</em></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft  wp-image-16024\" style=\"margin: 10px; border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"mobile for good look inside\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mobile-for-good-look-inside.jpg?resize=99%2C150\" width=\"99\" height=\"150\" /></a>Based on more than 20 years of experience and 25,000+ hours spent utilizing mobile and social media,\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><em><strong>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</strong></em></a>\u00a0is a comprehensive 256-page book packed with more than 500 best practices. Written on the premise that all communications and fundraising are now mobile and social, Mobile for Good is a step-by-step how-to guide for writing, implementing, and maintaining a mobile and social fundraising strategy for your nonprofit.<br />\n<strong>\u00a0</strong></p>\n",
